Title: oracle_dataguard_stats: Added option to specify the state if MRP is started
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1611048733
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

In some cases it is not sufficient to have the state hard coded in case the
Managed Recovery Process is started or stopped. With this werk you are able
to set the states in both cases if the default values are not reflecting
your requirements.
